General Information
===================

This is the 2.16.0 version of gedit-plugin-TLoleo. gedit-plugin-TLoleo are a set of plugins
for gedit.

Installation
============

You have to ./configure with --prefix=same prefix as you
configured gedit with.

How to choose which plugins to build:

./configure --with-plugins=pl1,pl2,...

where pl1, pl2 ... are one of the following:

TLoleo			Synthesizes the selected text with Festival using the Spanish male voice from Hispavoces project.

all			All of the above plugins
